{"id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0001", "text": "我對着青空許願 找一個寬廣的平原", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 2, 3, 3, 9, 2, 9, 3, 4, 3, 9, 3, 0, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "deoi3", "zoek6", "cing1", "hung1", "heoi2", "jyun6", "zaau2", "jat1", "go3", "fun1", "gwong2", "dik1", "ping4", "jyun4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "青空", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "許願", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "寬廣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "平原", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "光天化日", "artists": ["Wong"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3536", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0002", "text": "不需要磚 不須要穿 跟你 幸福愛戀", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 4, 3, 3, 3, 4, 3, 3, 5, 2, 3, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "seoi1", "jiu3", "zyun1", "bat1", "seoi1", "jiu3", "cyun1", "gan1", "nei5", "hang6", "fuk1", "oi3", "lyun2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "需要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "磚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "須要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "穿", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幸福", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛戀", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "光天化日", "artists": ["Wong"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3536", "prev_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0003", "text": "赤腳踏過青草地 烈日憑什麼好奇", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 4, 2, 4, 3, 9, 2, 2, 2, 0, 2, 3, 9, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cek3", "goek3", "daap6", "gwo3", "cing1", "cou2", "dei6", "lit6", "jat6", "pang4", "sam6", "mo1", "hou2", "kei4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "赤", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "腳踏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "青草地", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "烈日", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "憑", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "什麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好奇", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "光天化日", "artists": ["Wong"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3536", "prev_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0004", "text": "風箏要飛雙相戀至死 天公都造美", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 4, 3, 3, 9, 4, 9, 3, 3, 3, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["fung1", "zang1", "jiu3", "fei1", "soeng1", "lyun2", "zi3", "sei2", "tin1", "gung1", "dou1", "zou6", "mei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "風箏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "飛雙", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "相戀", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "至死", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天公", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "造美", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "光天化日", "artists": ["Wong"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3536", "prev_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0005", "text": "含着笑 我宣佈 共你高貴地擁抱", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 4, 5, 3, 4, 2, 5, 3, 4, 2, 9, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ham4", "zoek6", "siu3", "ngo5", "syun1", "bou3", "gung6", "nei5", "gou1", "gwai3", "dei6", "jung2", "pou5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "含着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "笑", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "宣佈", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "共", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高貴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "地", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "擁抱", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "光天化日", "artists": ["Wong"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3536", "prev_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0006", "text": "除下最漂亮錦袍 至少比蚯蚓驕傲", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 4, 3, 2, 9, 0, 4, 9, 3, 5, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ceoi4", "haa6", "zeoi3", "piu1", "loeng6", "gam2", "pou4", "zi3", "bei2", "jau1", "jan5", "giu1", "ngou6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "除下", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "漂亮", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "錦袍", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "至少", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "比", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "蚯蚓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "驕傲", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "光天化日", "artists": ["Wong"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3536", "prev_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0007", "text": "由我宣佈 共你於赤道起舞", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 3, 4, 2, 5, 3, 4, 2, 9, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jau4", "ngo5", "syun1", "bou3", "gung6", "nei5", "jyu1", "cek3", "dou6", "hei2", "mou5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "由", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "宣佈", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "共", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "於", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "赤道", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "起舞", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "光天化日", "artists": ["Wong"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3536", "prev_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0008", "text": "誰若有十字架 請找愛去比武的 去殉道", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 5, 2, 2, 9, 9, 9, 4, 4, 9, 5, 3, 4, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "joek6", "jau5", "sap6", "zi6", "gaa2", "cing2", "zaau2", "oi3", "heoi3", "bei2", "mou5", "dik1", "heoi3", "seon1", "dou6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "若", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "十字架", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "請", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "比武", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "殉道", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "光天化日", "artists": ["Wong"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3536", "prev_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0009", "text": "愛裏找不到恐懼 只恐怕找不到愛侶", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 5, 9, 3, 4, 9, 2, 9, 9, 4, 9, 3, 4, 4, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["oi3", "leoi5", "zaau2", "bat1", "dou3", "hung2", "geoi6", "zi2", "hung2", "paa3", "zaau2", "bat1", "dou3", "oi3", "leoi5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "愛裏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "恐懼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "恐怕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛侶", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "光天化日", "artists": ["Wong"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_3536", "prev_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_V29uZw_MzUzNg_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
